| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0786 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0d0dbfcf-0fd3-5a7f-8d88-bc1a1b637369"
